作者: CLARAAA (原來我的臉還不大)
標題: 珍惜此時此刻
時間: Thu Apr 22 15:21:35 1999



To realize the value of ONE YEAR,ask the student who has failed a class.
想知道「一整年」的價值,就去問被當過的學生

To realize the value of ONE MONTH,ask a mother who gave birth to a
premature baby.
想知道「一個月」的價值,就去問曾經早產的母親

To realize the value of ONE WEEK,ask the editor of a weekly newspaper.
想知道「一禮拜」的價值,就去問週報的編輯

To realize the value of ONE HOUR,ask the lovers who are waiting to meet.
想知道「一小時」的價值,就去問在等待見面的情侶

To realize the value of ONE MINUTE,ask a person who missed the train.
想知道「一分鐘」的價值,就去問剛錯過火車的人

To realize the value of ONE SECOND,ask a person who just avoided an
accident.
想知道「一秒鐘」的價值,就去問剛閃過一場車禍的人
To realize the value of ONE MILLISECOND,ask the person who won a silver

medal in the Olympics.
想知道「百分之一秒」的價值,就去問奧運的銀牌得主

Treasure every moment that you have!
珍惜你所擁有的每一刻時間

Yesterday is history. Tomorrow is mystery.
昨日已成歷史，而明日仍是個謎

Today is a gift.
今天是珍貴的禮物

That's why it's called the present!!
今天是珍貴的禮物

That's why it's called the present!!
那是它為何被稱做『當下』的原因

It's National Friendship Week.
現在是國際友誼週
Show your friends how much you care.....
讓你的朋友知道你有多在乎他們！

Send this to everyone you consider a FRIEND.
把這封信傳給所有你認為是朋友的人

If it comes back to you, then you'll know you have a circle of Friends.
如果這封信，又回到你的信箱，
你就會知道你有個無止盡...友誼的圓

HAPPY FRIENDSHIP WEEK!!!!!!!!                   快樂友誼週


          好看吧...

          但是希望你能更珍惜唷...

